paragraphs.title: 2.1: Regression
paragraphs.text:
%md
WNBA Player Stats Season 2016-2017
Dataset URL: https://www.kaggle.com/jinxbe/wnba-player-stats-2017

import org.apache.spark.ml.feature.Interaction
import org.apache.spark.ml.feature.VectorAssembler
import org.apache.spark.ml.linalg.{Matrix, Vectors}
import org.apache.spark.ml.stat.Correlation
import org.apache.spark.sql.Row
import org.apache.spark.ml.regression.LinearRegression

val data = spark.read.format("csv").option("header", "true").option("inferSchema", "true").load("C:/Users/merth/Desktop/WNBA.csv")
val df = data.select(data.columns.slice(11, 30).map(col(_)): _*)
df.show()

val assembler = new VectorAssembler().
  setInputCols(Array( "Games Played","FGM", "FGA", "FG%", "15:00", "3PA", "3P%", "FTM", "FTA","FT%", "OREB", "DREB", "REB", "AST", "STL", "BLK", "TO", "PTS")).
  setOutputCol("features").
  transform(df)

assembler.show()
val Array(trainingData, testData) = assembler.randomSplit(Array(0.8, 0.2))

msg.data:
trainingData: org.apache.spark.sql.Dataset[org.apache.spark.sql.Row] = [Games Played: int, MIN: int ... 18 more fields]
testData: org.apache.spark.sql.Dataset[org.apache.spark.sql.Row] = [Games Played: int, MIN: int ... 18 more fields]

paragraphs.text:
val lr = new LinearRegression()
  .setLabelCol("MIN")
  .setFeaturesCol("features")
  .setMaxIter(100)
  .setRegParam(1.0)
  .setElasticNetParam(1.0)
  
val lrModel = lr.fit(trainingData)

lrModel.transform(testData).select("features","MIN", "prediction").show()

val trainingSummary = lrModel.summary
println(s"numIterations: ${trainingSummary.totalIterations}")
println(s"RMSE: ${trainingSummary.rootMeanSquaredError}")
println(s"R2 Score: ${trainingSummary.r2}")

val corr_features = new VectorAssembler().
  setInputCols(Array( "Games Played","MIN","FGM", "FGA", "FG%", "15:00", "3PA", "3P%", "FTM", "FTA","FT%", "OREB", "DREB", "REB", "AST", "STL", "BLK", "TO", "PTS")).
  setOutputCol("features").
  transform(df)

val correlation_matrix = Correlation.corr(corr_features, "features").head

println("Pearson correlation matrix:\n" + correlation_matrix.toString)

paragraphs.title: 2.2: Classification
paragraphs.text:
%md
Chronic Kidney Disease
Dataset URL: https://archive.ics.uci.edu/ml/datasets/Chronic_Kidney_Disease

val ckd = spark.read.format("csv").option("header", "true").option("inferSchema", "true").load("C:/Users/merth/Desktop/chronic_kidney_disease.csv")

val ckd_df = new VectorAssembler()
    .setInputCols(Array("age","bp","sg","al","su","rbc","pc","pcc","ba","bgr","bu","sc","sod","pot","hemo","pcv","wbcc","rbcc","htn","dm","cad","appet","pe","ane"))
    .setOutputCol("features")
    .transform(ckd)

ckd_df.show()
val Array(trainingData, testData) = ckd_df.randomSplit(Array(0.7, 0.3))

msg.data:
trainingData: org.apache.spark.sql.Dataset[org.apache.spark.sql.Row] = [age: double, bp: double ... 24 more fields]
testData: org.apache.spark.sql.Dataset[org.apache.spark.sql.Row] = [age: double, bp: double ... 24 more fields]

paragraphs.text:
import org.apache.spark.ml.classification.LogisticRegression

val logr = new LogisticRegression()
    .setLabelCol("class")
    .setFeaturesCol("features")
    .setRegParam(0.3)
    .setElasticNetParam(0.8)
    .setMaxIter(10)
    
val logrModel = logr.fit(trainingData)

logrModel.transform(testData).select("features","class", "prediction").show()

import org.apache.spark.ml.evaluation.MulticlassClassificationEvaluator

val logr_pred = logrModel.transform(testData)

logr_pred.select("prediction", "class", "features").show(5)

val logr_eval = new MulticlassClassificationEvaluator()
  .setLabelCol("class")
  .setPredictionCol("prediction")
  .setMetricName("accuracy")
val Accuracy = logr_eval.evaluate(logr_pred)

paragraphs.title: 3.3 : Clustering
paragraphs.text:
%md
FIFA 18
Dataset URL: https://www.kaggle.com/oliversinn/fifa-18-visualisation-clustering-ml/data

val player_data = spark.read.format("csv").option("header", "true").option("inferSchema", "true").load("C:/Users/merth/Desktop/PlayerPlayingPositionData.csv")
player_data.show()

import org.apache.spark.ml.clustering.KMeans
val data_k = new VectorAssembler()
    .setInputCols(Array("CAM","CB","CDM","CF","CM","LAM","LB","LCB","LCM","LDM","LF","LM","LS","LW","LWB","RAM","RB","RCB","RCM","RDM","RF","RM","RS","RW","RWB","ST"))
    .setOutputCol("features")
    .transform(player_data)
  
val kmeans = new KMeans().setK(5).setSeed(1L).setFeaturesCol("features")
val kmodel = kmeans.fit(data_k)

val WSSSE = kmodel.computeCost(data_k)
println(s"Within Set Sum of Squared Errors = $WSSSE")


println("Cluster Centers: ")
kmodel.clusterCenters.foreach(println)
